					"type": 23,
					"value": "Repro steps:\r\n1. Start the game\r\n2. loadlevel WLD_Main_A\r\n3. oe readyattackonden\r\n4. goto 195.23, 34.85, 441.72 and skip through the entreance cinematic.\r\n5. Kill Zevlor (CTRL-K)\r\n6. Blow the horn and side with the tieflings.\r\n7. Killcombat\r\n8. Wait for the cinematic to start."
				},
